  <body>
  
    <section name="Create design">

      <p>This module allow to easly create a design file from a list of file (reads in fastq format, genome in fasta, annotation in gff).</p>  

      <ul>
         <li><b>Available</b>: Only in local mode.</li>
         <li><b>Optional parameters</b>:

	<table>
		<tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th><th>Description</th></tr>
		<tr><td>-output</td><td>a filename</td><td>The name of new design file</td></tr>
		<tr><td>-stdout</td><td>none</td><td>The generated design file will be return on stdout rather than in a file</td></tr>
	</table>
        </li>
        <li><b>Usage</b>:
<source>
$ eoulsan.sh [options] createdesign fastq_files fasta_file gff_gfile
</source>

</li>
        
       </ul>
      
    </section>


  </body>
  
